msgstr "https://github.com/burnoutberni/everycal"

#. Description of the plugin
#: everycal.php
msgid ""
"Display federated event feeds from any EveryCal server. Just add the "
"Gutenberg block and point it at a feed URL."
msgstr ""

#. Author of the plugin
#: everycal.php
#, fuzzy
